Former BBNaija ‘Lockdown’ season 5 housemate, Kiddwaya has disclosed his preference in terms of a life partner.  In a video during a live chat session with DJ Cuppy shared by Kiddwaya on his Instagram page, the billionaire son explained his kind of woman must be someone who possesses a big heart among other attributes. While Cuppy lamented about most guys not being attracted to girls with short hair, Kiddwaya revealed he is different as he loves women with short hair. “I like short hair women, I think it’s great”, he said. When eventually quizzed about his kind of woman, the reality TV star said: “I want someone with a big heart. That’s the only big thing I need. “Personality too because she’s gonna be the mother of my child. So you need to have for me, a great heart, God-fearing. “And I think you need to have great physical awareness. Awareness of what’s happening in the world.”   Source Kiddwaya, the evicted Big Brother Naija, BBNaija housemate, has cleared the air on his intentions for billionaire’s daughter, Dj Cuppy. Kiddwaya during his time in the BBNaija house mentioned Dj Cuppy a lot of times to housemates.   When asked if he would have an intimate relationship with Otedola’s daughter,… In "Entertainment" Kiddwaya, a Big Brother Naija housemate, has revealed the women in his life whom he is comfortable with and has equally shown his emotional side to. Kiddwaya had earlier made it known to Erica that he had no serious plans to continue with their relationship outside the house. He further… In "Entertainment" Terrywaya, The billionaire father of Big Brother Naija (BBNaija) housemate, Kiddwaya, has disclosed that if his son should win the competition, he would ensure he gives Erica, half of the price money. Terry Waya revealed that Erica’s disqualification came as a surprise and pained him a lot. He made this… In "Entertainment"